93.1096, 193.102, 192.9804, 192.9526, 193.4083, 194.6523, 192.7248, 194.0284, 194.2494, 193.1238, 192.7997, 194.8216, 194.9413, 196.5336, 195.7535, 195.8462, 196.1285, 196.6882, 198.1639, 196.9169, 198.1307, 198.542, 197.9848, 199.515, 199.3129, 200.8275, 201.6255, 202.3628, 202.107, 202.9868, 200.9685, 199.8789, 201.3438, 202.0579, 201.4845, 201.5027, 201.7571, 202.7193, 201.2896, 201.4229, 201.9086, 200.0886, 199.95, 200.2141, 199.8249, 200.9821, 200.3436, 198.987, 199.1903, 199.9214, 199.4716, 199.1931, 198.4288, 199.5334, 199.113, 199.0117, 198.8608, 199.1066, 198.857, 197.3288, 199.1342, 200.5281, 200.6236, 199.401, 201.722, 199.064, 198.9213, 198.5548, 197.4966, 196.2372, 196.4382, 195.254, 196.7976, 196.5975, 195.0615, 194.0913, 191.6726, 191.6998, 190.4978, 190.3326, 190.224, 190.0007, 190.547, 191.2034, 190.9766, 191.8019, 192.9108, 193.7953, 194.6245, 195.1751, 195.0034, 194.9688, 194.2875, 195.1687, 194.6556, 194.8077, 194.3627, 195.4431, 195.067, 196.0244, 195.3475, 195.2883, 196.5933, 197.1765, 196.0183, 195.9576, 198.8928, 197.7028, 198.1889, 198.5214, 199.7198, 199.2872, 201.7749, 201.0577, 200.742, 199.0602, 201.1108, 201.8838, 202.5268, 202.7768, 202.0377, 202.513, 204.0886, 203.9022, 205.1875, 205.9203, 207.0627, 206.6891, 207.5843, 207.8331, 207.0556, 205.871, 206.3531, 207.47, 209.7994, 211.1204, 211.7108, 214.173, 213.5923, 213.8834, 213.8553, 216.4623, 215.8683, 215.8085, 215.962, 216.6701, 217.2313, 216.0522, 217.689, 216.7228, 216.3782, 216.3244, 216.4355, 216.2076, 215.1442, 214.6724, 215.8682, 217.7355, 218.3382, 217.0666, 215.6779, 217.4902, 217.0025, 218.7421, 220.0649, 220.0977, 222.7055, 224.4584, 223.6795, 222.0901, 220.6776, 219.8532, 219.2487, 219.0989, 218.6646, 219.2325, 218.3656, 219.3335, 220.9743, 220.7877, 221.629, 221.5292, 222.4212, 223.925, 224.1123, 225.9887, 226.9442, 228.6396, 226.9449, 227.2373, 227.1962, 226.1658, 223.4203, 223.5873, 224.948, 225.4755, 226.1273, 225.5205, 226.8138, 227.6623, 226.626, 230.4731, 231.6233, 230.4013, 228.872, 229.729, 236.0828, 240.2073, 238.6682, 240.5503, 244.6265, 246.3772, 244.6637, 247.5644, 246.5431, 247.4974, 247.0389, 248.0238, 247.6519, 250.1428, 248.4598, 247.9128, 247.3756, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>商品多因子模型研究框架初探</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本研报系统梳理了商品期货多因子模型的研究框架，覆盖7大类因子：动量、期限结构、库存、套保压力、持仓、波动率、流动性。R1-R3 聚焦于期限结构（basis）因子，R4-R5 专攻持仓/库存/流动性等非carry维度的修正与优化。</p>\n<p><strong>核心发现</strong>：库存因子的方向纠正和窗口拉长是本次迭代的关键突破。原始实现中库存变化率为正=库存增加=做多，但正确的经济逻辑是低库存=供给紧缺=看涨。将库存因子翻转方向并改用252日z-score后，Sharpe从-0.57跃升至1.37，同时会员持仓因子也从-0.44改善至+0.41。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.38</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.0%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-7.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.04</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2947</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.37</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>2.87</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.33 / 1.42</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.49</td><td>0.09</td><td>1.59</td><td>1.03</td><td>0.36</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.83</span></td><td>1.41</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.06</span></td><td>1.63</td><td>0.73</td><td>0.79</td><td>1.1</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">5.17</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>58</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2949</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>97.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>32.5</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<h3>核心因子（负库存z-score）</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{inv\\_neg}_{i,t} = -\\frac{\\ln(\\text{inv}_{i,t}) - \\mu_{i,t}^{252}}{\\sigma_{i,t}^{252}}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\mu_{i,t}^{252}</span> 和 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_{i,t}^{252}</span> 是品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 过去252个交易日库存对数值的滚动均值和标准差。负号确保低库存品种获得高因子值。</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_i = \\text{rank}(\\text{inv\\_neg}_i) \\in [0, 1]</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_i = (\\text{rank}_i - 0.5) \\times 2 \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{target}}}{\\hat{\\sigma}_i}</div>\n<h3>会员持仓因子（修正版）</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{memb\\_lvl}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{memberdiff20}_{i,t}}{\\text{OI}_{i,t}}</div>\n<p>前20名会员净多空差占总持仓比例。正值=多头占优=看涨信号。</p>\n<h3>基本面组合</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{fundE} = \\frac{1}{3}\\left(\\text{rank}(\\text{inv\\_neg252}) + \\text{rank}(\\text{basis}) + \\text{rank}(\\text{ry})\\right)</div>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>basis因子0.79, 换手率1.03过高</td><td>增加basis hold=20, carry组合</td><td><strong>basis20=0.83 突破0.8</strong>, 换手降至0.45</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>触发CS/TS归一化</td><td>自动添加_cs/_ts变体(63个)</td><td>未超越raw, basis20仍最优0.83</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>3轮最低要求达标</td><td>维持不变</td><td>decision=skip</td></tr><tr><td>R4</td><td>持仓/库存/流动性因子全部负Sharpe</td><td><strong>方向修正</strong>: inv取负(低库存=bullish), memb_lvl用水平而非变化率, Amihud取负</td><td>inv_neg: -0.57-&gt;+0.58, memb_lvl: -0.44-&gt;+0.41, fundcombo=0.60</td></tr><tr><td>R5</td><td>inv_neg最优0.58, 需扩大参数网格</td><td>252日窗口z-score + 多持仓期网格 + 基本面组合</td><td><strong>inv_neg252_10=1.37</strong>, 突破性提升</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>: 1. R1: hold_days从5增至20，通过降低换手率使basis因子突破0.8 2. R4: 发现库存、会员持仓因子<strong>方向完全反了</strong>。库存增加应看空而非看多，memberdiff20水平值而非变化率才有经济含义 3. R5: 库存z-score窗口从60日拉长至252日，从0.58跳至1.37。年度窗口捕捉库存季节性周期，远优于短期噪声</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（56个有库存数据的商品期货）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 10天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>核心数据</strong>: <code>inventory_21</code>（库存21日口径，非空率约71%）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 与因子库 <code>20141201_tianfeng_inv21_zs252_h42_raw</code> (Sharpe 1.54) 相关性0.75，verdict为 <code>likely_redundant</code> -- 本质上是同一因子逻辑（库存z-score，252日窗口）\n<p>- 2023年和2025年Sharpe接近0，库存因子在商品市场平静期效果偏弱 - 库存数据非空率71%，部分品种（如金融期货）无库存数据</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>K</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>base lookback (unused for inv_neg252 but kept for context)</td></tr><tr><td><code>INV_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>252</code></td><td>inventory z-score window</td></tr><tr><td><code>INV_MIN_PERIODS</code></td><td><code>84</code></td><td>max(252 // 3, 10)</td></tr><tr><td><code>SCALE</code></td><td><code>2.0</code></td><td>rank_to_continuous scale</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.18s</li>\n</ul>"}